      <title>丹麦部长探讨利用乌克兰基金加速武器生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/denmark-defense-minister-explores-ukraine-fund-to-hasten-weapons-output</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦国防部长特洛尔斯·伦德·波尔森表示，丹麦正计划设立一个基金来集中投资，扩大乌克兰的武器工业并加快制造速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/denmark-defense-minister-explores-ukraine-fund-to-hasten-weapons-output</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 13:29:39 GMT</pubDate>
